      "@id": "https://mikki-mase.com/banned#article",
      "headline": "Mikki Mase Banned From 150+ Casinos - Interactive Map & Complete List",
      "description": "Interactive map showing all 150+ casinos that banned Mikki Mase. Includes legal framework, absurd ban reasons, and detailed casino locations.",
